[{"id":"77c61621484e27e14323e6b7a873a66b","from":"Petra Nemcova","from_email":"petranemcova@bethelightny.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Summertime fun... What's next?","date":"2014-09-15T18:20:17.000Z","formatted_date":"Sep 15, 2014","formatted_time":"6:20 PM","body":"\nDear friends,\n\nI hope this note finds you well-rested after an exciting summer filled with travel\nand inspiration!\n\nI'm writing to you today because autumn is approaching, and as the year winds down\nto an end, it's a great time to look back at what good deeds you've done this year.\n;) - or what opportunities lie ahead :)\n\nWould you like to help bring hope to children who have been impacted by natural \ndisaster and who are still waiting for new schools? Sometimes they wait 4-6 years.\nWith Happy Hearts Fund, we have already rebuilt 90 save-resilient schools for children\nin 9 countries.\n\nFollow this link and see how you can help in fun way.\n\nhttp://happyheartsfund.org/welcome-back/ [http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001dyx9HdkVhd1V_RiqrEq5LAfRSx_jkk7NEOW7xZRGecjkle7tjONVC6GUJCdodnGRuGvUqNkAAoe6H13uBqXqKLA-Db4H-4iR164p0QG8yCtALh_My3HzHeSuV8HvN-JJHgWbPdmdFqnsouP-NgY3_EQlHFfTlzO7G-NXtNcjiZINMSv_gzNq-3hcgPUK2dZXOlInz7HZqQM=&c=w_rWE6py-JNF2stCJilNMjgkAuhQgNG4fpD6VmWL_i_JtLG4_VMhEA==&ch=MCHi5hqv3Ms0ipCqc-g3mFEtgCGbEQnPkaNp3OYBYg6wd-CittjB5w==]\n\nThank you from bottom of my heart. :*)\n\nLots of Love, Light and Laughter\nPetra Nemcova\nAmbassador at Large for Haiti & Founder and Chair, Happy Hearts Fund\n2014 marks the 10 year anniversary of the Indian Ocean Tsunami. Thanks to your support,\nHappy Hearts Fund will commemorate this event by rebuilding our 100th safe-resilient\nschool by the end of this year! Because of your incredible support, we just opened\nthe 90th school. To see them and learn what you have accomplished with Happy Hearts\nFund thus far, take a look here. https://vimeo.com/10284414