gn=\"left\"><span>I'm writing to you today because autumn is approaching, and as the year winds down to an end, it's a great time to look back at what good deeds you've done this year. ;) - or what opportunities lie ahead :)&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><span>Would you like to help bring hope to children who have been impacted by natural disaster and who are still waiting for new schools? Sometimes they wait 4-6 years.&nbsp;</span>With Happy Hearts Fund, we have already rebuilt&nbsp;90 save-resilient schools for children in 9 countries.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><span>Follow this link and see how you can help in fun way.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" track=\"on\" shape=\"rect\" href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001dyx9HdkVhd1V_RiqrEq5LAfRSx_jkk7NEOW7xZRGecjkle7tjONVC6GUJCdodnGRuGvUqNkAAoe6H13uBqXqKLA-Db4H-4iR164p0QG8yCtALh_My3HzHeSuV8HvN-JJHgWbPdmdFqnsouP-NgY3_EQlHFfTlzO7G-NXtNcjiZINMSv_gzNq-3hcgPUK2dZXOlInz7HZqQM=&c=w_rWE6py-JNF2stCJilNMjgkAuhQgNG4fpD6VmWL_i_JtLG4_VMhEA==&ch=MCHi5hqv3Ms0ipCqc-g3mFEtgCGbEQnPkaNp3OYBYg6wd-CittjB5w==\" linktype=\"1\" target=\"_blank\">http://happyheartsfund.org/welcome-back/</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><span>Thank you from bottom of my heart. :*)</span></p>\n</div><div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\">Lots of Love, Light and Laughter</div><div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><br /><div>Petra Nemcova&nbsp;</div><br /><div>Ambassador at Large for Haiti & Founder and Chair, Happy Hearts Fund</div><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"left\"><span>2014 marks the 10 year anniversary of the Indian Ocean Tsunami. Thanks to your support,&nbsp;<a shape=\"rect\">Happy Hearts Fund</a>&nbsp;will commemorate this event by rebuilding our 100th safe-resilient school by the end of this year! Because of your incredible support, we just opened the 90th school. To see them and learn what you have accomplished with Happy Hearts Fund thus far, take a look here.&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" track=\"on\" shape=\"rect\" href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001dyx9HdkVhd1V_RiqrEq5LAfRSx_jkk7NEOW7xZRGecjkle7tjONVC6GUJCdodnGR4vuQBeXoGNZki_Y3x4ZVCnzmU8VJwPgCEjylCKg3u8teDg62TIrFlnvuth7bIhjWkbI_DE7ODuSva3bcoQlQWVB8IJwbfO-dJiMjYLpGofjK1vJaw0dZGg==&c=w_rWE6py-JNF2stCJilNMjgkAuhQgNG4fpD6VmWL_i_JtLG4_VMhEA==&ch=MCHi5hqv3Ms0ipCqc-g3mFEtgCGbEQnPkaNp3OYBYg6wd-CittjB5w==\" linktype=\"1\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/102844145</a><span>.&nbsp;</span></div><br /><div><br /> <br /></div></td></tr></table></td>\n\n </tr>\n </table>\n\n </td>\n <td valign=\"bottom\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><img height=\"5\" vspace=\"0\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://img.constantcontact.com/letters/images/1101116784221/S.gif\" /></td>\n </tr>\n </table>\n </div>\n </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n <td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\" align=\